actions.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

official_title: To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to repeal the excise tax on telephone and other communications services.
short_title: Telephone Excise Tax Repeal Act of 2005

summary.text: Telephone Excise Tax Repeal Act of 2005 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to repeal the excise tax on communication services (i.e., local telephone service, toll telephone service, and teletypewriter exchange service).

titles.title: Telephone Excise Tax Repeal Act of 2005
